Hi @razzeee,
I have installed the [parcel-svg-plugin](https://github.com/ChristophP/parcel-transformer-elm-svg-modules) and have replaced the logo png files with svgs. 
It would be great if you could review it, Thank you.

![Screenshot from 2022-06-30 22-55-14](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/18377109/176740191-c4ddca97-56cb-42f2-ac56-2f601ebb82fd.png)
